HQL_COUNT_DISTINCT.name: HQL_COUNT_DISTINCT
HQL_COUNT_DISTINCT.queryString: SELECT count(distinct A.classTeacher) AS COUNT_DISTINCT_CLASSTEACHER FROM Academics A

HQL_GroupBy.name: HQL_GroupBy
HQL_GroupBy.queryString: SELECT SUM(R.marksSecured) as SUM_MARKS, R.academicYear AS ACADEMIC_YEAR,R.studentId AS STUDENT_ID FROM Results R  GROUP BY R.studentId

SV_AVGFunction.name: SV_AVGFunction
SV_AVGFunction.queryString: select avg(MARKS_SECURED) from RESULTS where STUDENT_ID=:STUDENT_ID
SV_AVGFunction.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select avg(MARKS_SECURED) from RESULTS where STUDENT_ID=:STUDENT_ID) wmTempTable

SV_Alias.name: SV_Alias
SV_Alias.queryString: select R.ACADEMIC_YEAR AS R_ACADEMIC_YEAR,R.STANDARD_ID AS R_STANDARD_ID,R.STUDENT_ID AS R_STUDENT_ID,R.MARKS_SECURED AS R_MARKS_SECURED,R.GRADE_ID AS R_GRADE_ID,ATS.* from RESULTS R, ACADEMIC_TEST_SUBJECTS ATS
SV_Alias.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select R.ACADEMIC_YEAR AS R_ACADEMIC_YEAR,R.STANDARD_ID AS R_STANDARD_ID,R.STUDENT_ID AS R_STUDENT_ID,R.MARKS_SECURED AS R_MARKS_SECURED,R.GRADE_ID AS R_GRADE_ID,ATS.* from RESULTS R, ACADEMIC_TEST_SUBJECTS ATS) wmTempTable

SV_ConcatQuery.name: SV_ConcatQuery
SV_ConcatQuery.queryString: select EMP_ID,CONCAT(FIRSTNAME,'.',LASTNAME) AS FULL_NAME,CONCAT(STATE,', ',CITY,', ',STREET,', ',ZIP) AS ADDRESS,DATE_OF_BIRTH from EMPLOYEE_DETAILS
SV_ConcatQuery.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select EMP_ID,CONCAT(FIRSTNAME,'.',LASTNAME) AS FULL_NAME,CONCAT(STATE,', ',CITY,', ',STREET,', ',ZIP) AS ADDRESS,DATE_OF_BIRTH from EMPLOYEE_DETAILS) wmTempTable

SV_CountSyntax.name: SV_CountSyntax
SV_CountSyntax.queryString: select count(STUDENT_ID) from RESULTS where TEST_CONDUCTED_ID=2
SV_CountSyntax.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select count(STUDENT_ID) from RESULTS where TEST_CONDUCTED_ID=2) wmTempTable

SV_DateFormatSyntax.name: SV_DateFormatSyntax
SV_DateFormatSyntax.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select FIRSTNAME,LASTNAME,DATE_FORMAT(DATE_OF_BIRTH,'%a %D %b %Y') as DATE_OF_BIRTH from EMPLOYEE_DETAILS) wmTempTable

SV_FullJoin.name: SV_FullJoin
SV_FullJoin.queryString:
select R.STUDENT_ID,R.MARKS_SECURED,R.GRADE_ID,R.TEST_CONDUCTED_ID,ATS.MAX_MARKS,ATS.SUBJECT_ID from RESULTS R LEFT OUTER JOIN ACADEMIC_TEST_SUBJECTS ATS ON R.ACADEMIC_YEAR=ATS.ACADEMIC_YEAR AND R.STANDARD_ID=ATS.STANDARD_ID
UNION ALL
select R.STUDENT_ID,R.MARKS_SECURED,R.GRADE_ID,R.TEST_CONDUCTED_ID,ATS.MAX_MARKS,ATS.SUBJECT_ID from RESULTS R RIGHT OUTER JOIN ACADEMIC_TEST_SUBJECTS ATS ON R.ACADEMIC_YEAR=ATS.ACADEMIC_YEAR AND R.STANDARD_ID=ATS.STANDARD_ID
SV_FullJoin.countQueryString:
select count(*) from (select R.STUDENT_ID,R.MARKS_SECURED,R.GRADE_ID,R.TEST_CONDUCTED_ID,ATS.MAX_MARKS,ATS.SUBJECT_ID from RESULTS R LEFT OUTER JOIN ACADEMIC_TEST_SUBJECTS ATS ON R.ACADEMIC_YEAR=ATS.ACADEMIC_YEAR AND R.STANDARD_ID=ATS.STANDARD_ID
UNION ALL
select R.STUDENT_ID,R.MARKS_SECURED,R.GRADE_ID,R.TEST_CONDUCTED_ID,ATS.MAX_MARKS,ATS.SUBJECT_ID from RESULTS R RIGHT OUTER JOIN ACADEMIC_TEST_SUBJECTS ATS ON R.ACADEMIC_YEAR=ATS.ACADEMIC_YEAR AND R.STANDARD_ID=ATS.STANDARD_ID) wmTempTable

SV_GroupBy.name: SV_GroupBy
SV_GroupBy.queryString: select sum(R.MARKS_SECURED) as MARKS_SECURED,R.STUDENT_ID,R.TEST_CONDUCTED_ID,ACADEMIC_YEAR,STANDARD_ID from RESULTS R where R.ACADEMIC_YEAR=:ACADEMIC_YEAR and R.STANDARD_ID=1 GROUP BY STUDENT_ID
SV_GroupBy.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select sum(R.MARKS_SECURED) as MARKS_SECURED,R.STUDENT_ID,R.TEST_CONDUCTED_ID,ACADEMIC_YEAR,STANDARD_ID from RESULTS R where R.ACADEMIC_YEAR=:ACADEMIC_YEAR and R.STANDARD_ID=1 GROUP BY STUDENT_ID) wmTempTable

SV_GroupByHavingClause.name: SV_GroupByHavingClause
SV_GroupByHavingClause.queryString: select sum(R.MARKS_SECURED) as MARKS_SECURED,R.STUDENT_ID,R.TEST_CONDUCTED_ID,ACADEMIC_YEAR,STANDARD_ID from RESULTS R where R.ACADEMIC_YEAR=:ACADEMIC_YEAR and R.STANDARD_ID=1 GROUP BY STUDENT_ID HAVING MARKS_SECURED>700
SV_GroupByHavingClause.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select sum(R.MARKS_SECURED) as MARKS_SECURED,R.STUDENT_ID,R.TEST_CONDUCTED_ID,ACADEMIC_YEAR,STANDARD_ID from RESULTS R where R.ACADEMIC_YEAR=:ACADEMIC_YEAR and R.STANDARD_ID=1 GROUP BY STUDENT_ID HAVING MARKS_SECURED>700) wmTempTable

SV_InnerJoinWithOrderBy.name: SV_InnerJoinWithOrderBy
SV_InnerJoinWithOrderBy.queryString: select E.*,U.* from EMPLOYEE_DETAILS E INNER JOIN USER_LOGIN U ON E.EMP_ID=U.USER_ID ORDER BY E.FIRSTNAME ASC
SV_InnerJoinWithOrderBy.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select E.*,U.* from EMPLOYEE_DETAILS E INNER JOIN USER_LOGIN U ON E.EMP_ID=U.USER_ID ORDER BY E.FIRSTNAME ASC) wmTempTable

SV_InnerJoins.name: SV_InnerJoins
SV_InnerJoins.queryString:
SELECT R.*,A.CLASS_TEACHER,A.CLASS_ROOM,ACS.SUBJECT_ID,ACS.SUBJECT_TEACHER,ATS.TEST_ID,ATS.MAX_MARKS 
FROM RESULTS R 
INNER JOIN ACADEMICS A ON R.ACADEMIC_YEAR=A.ACADEMIC_YEAR AND R.STANDARD_ID=A.STANDARD_ID 
INNER JOIN ACADEMIC_SUBJECTS ACS ON ACS.ACADEMIC_YEAR=R.ACADEMIC_YEAR AND ACS.STANDARD_ID=R.STANDARD_ID
INNER JOIN ACADEMIC_TEST_SUBJECTS ATS ON ATS.ACADEMIC_YEAR=R.ACADEMIC_YEAR AND ATS.STANDARD_ID=R.STANDARD_ID
SV_InnerJoins.countQueryString:
select count(*) from (SELECT R.*,A.CLASS_TEACHER,A.CLASS_ROOM,ACS.SUBJECT_ID,ACS.SUBJECT_TEACHER,ATS.TEST_ID,ATS.MAX_MARKS 
FROM RESULTS R 
INNER JOIN ACADEMICS A ON R.ACADEMIC_YEAR=A.ACADEMIC_YEAR AND R.STANDARD_ID=A.STANDARD_ID 
INNER JOIN ACADEMIC_SUBJECTS ACS ON ACS.ACADEMIC_YEAR=R.ACADEMIC_YEAR AND ACS.STANDARD_ID=R.STANDARD_ID
INNER JOIN ACADEMIC_TEST_SUBJECTS ATS ON ATS.ACADEMIC_YEAR=R.ACADEMIC_YEAR AND ATS.STANDARD_ID=R.STANDARD_ID) wmTempTable

SV_IsNULL.name: SV_IsNULL
SV_IsNULL.queryString: SELECT * FROM RESULTS Where  PRESENCE IS NULL
SV_IsNULL.countQueryString: select count(*) from (SELECT * FROM RESULTS Where  PRESENCE IS NULL) wmTempTable

SV_LeftOuterJoin.name: SV_LeftOuterJoin
SV_LeftOuterJoin.queryString: select ATS.*,A.CLASS_ROOM,A.CLASS_TEACHER from ACADEMIC_TEST_SUBJECTS ATS LEFT OUTER JOIN ACADEMICS A ON ATS.ACADEMIC_YEAR=A.ACADEMIC_YEAR AND ATS.STANDARD_ID=A.STANDARD_ID
SV_LeftOuterJoin.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select ATS.*,A.CLASS_ROOM,A.CLASS_TEACHER from ACADEMIC_TEST_SUBJECTS ATS LEFT OUTER JOIN ACADEMICS A ON ATS.ACADEMIC_YEAR=A.ACADEMIC_YEAR AND ATS.STANDARD_ID=A.STANDARD_ID) wmTempTable

SV_LengthFunction.name: SV_LengthFunction
SV_LengthFunction.queryString: SELECT DISTINCT ADDRESS,LENGTH(ADDRESS) AS ADDRESS_LENGTH FROM STUDENT_DETAILS
SV_LengthFunction.countQueryString: select count(*) from (SELECT DISTINCT ADDRESS,LENGTH(ADDRESS) AS ADDRESS_LENGTH FROM STUDENT_DETAILS) wmTempTable

SV_LowerFunction.name: SV_LowerFunction
SV_LowerFunction.queryString: select LCASE(FIRSTNAME) AS FIRSTNAME,LOWER(LASTNAME) AS LASTNAME from EMPLOYEE_DETAILS
SV_LowerFunction.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select LCASE(FIRSTNAME) AS FIRSTNAME,LOWER(LASTNAME) AS LASTNAME from EMPLOYEE_DETAILS) wmTempTable

SV_MAXFunction.name: SV_MAXFunction
SV_MAXFunction.queryString: select MAX(MARKS_SECURED) from RESULTS WHERE ACADEMIC_YEAR=:ACADEMIC_YEAR AND STANDARD_ID=1 AND TEST_CONDUCTED_ID=1
SV_MAXFunction.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select MAX(MARKS_SECURED) from RESULTS WHERE ACADEMIC_YEAR=:ACADEMIC_YEAR AND STANDARD_ID=1 AND TEST_CONDUCTED_ID=1) wmTempTable

SV_MinFunction.name: SV_MinFunction
SV_MinFunction.queryString: select MIN(MARKS_SECURED) from RESULTS WHERE ACADEMIC_YEAR=:ACADEMIC_YEAR AND STANDARD_ID=1 AND TEST_CONDUCTED_ID=1
SV_MinFunction.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select MIN(MARKS_SECURED) from RESULTS WHERE ACADEMIC_YEAR=:ACADEMIC_YEAR AND STANDARD_ID=1 AND TEST_CONDUCTED_ID=1) wmTempTable

SV_NOTNULL.name: SV_NOTNULL
SV_NOTNULL.queryString: SELECT * FROM RESULTS Where PRESENCE IS NOT NULL
SV_NOTNULL.countQueryString: select count(*) from (SELECT * FROM RESULTS Where PRESENCE IS NOT NULL) wmTempTable

SV_NestedQuery.name: SV_NestedQuery
SV_NestedQuery.queryString: select * from RESULTS WHERE TEST_CONDUCTED_ID=(select TEST_CONDUCTED_ID from TEST_CONDUCTED where ACADEMIC_YEAR=:ACADEMIC_YEAR and STANDARD_ID=1 and SUBJECT_ID=1 and TEST_ID=3)
SV_NestedQuery.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select * from RESULTS WHERE TEST_CONDUCTED_ID=(select TEST_CONDUCTED_ID from TEST_CONDUCTED where ACADEMIC_YEAR=:ACADEMIC_YEAR and STANDARD_ID=1 and SUBJECT_ID=1 and TEST_ID=3)) wmTempTable

SV_QueryWithDate.name: SV_QueryWithDate
SV_QueryWithDate.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select * from STUDENT_DETAILS where JOINING_DATE=:JDATE) wmTempTable

SV_RightJoin.name: SV_RightJoin
SV_RightJoin.queryString: select ATS.*,A.CLASS_ROOM,A.CLASS_TEACHER from ACADEMIC_TEST_SUBJECTS ATS RIGHT OUTER JOIN ACADEMICS A ON ATS.ACADEMIC_YEAR=A.ACADEMIC_YEAR AND ATS.STANDARD_ID=A.STANDARD_ID
SV_RightJoin.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select ATS.*,A.CLASS_ROOM,A.CLASS_TEACHER from ACADEMIC_TEST_SUBJECTS ATS RIGHT OUTER JOIN ACADEMICS A ON ATS.ACADEMIC_YEAR=A.ACADEMIC_YEAR AND ATS.STANDARD_ID=A.STANDARD_ID) wmTempTable

SV_StudentDetails.name: SV_StudentDetails
SV_StudentDetails.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select * from STUDENT_DETAILS) wmTempTable

SV_SubStr.name: SV_SubStr
SV_SubStr.queryString: select substr(CITY,1,8) as SHORTEN_CITY from EMPLOYEE_DETAILS
SV_SubStr.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select substr(CITY,1,8) as SHORTEN_CITY from EMPLOYEE_DETAILS) wmTempTable

SV_SumFunction.name: SV_SumFunction
SV_SumFunction.queryString: select sum(MARKS_SECURED) as TOTAL_MARKS_SECURED, STUDENT_ID from RESULTS where ACADEMIC_YEAR=:ACADEMIC_YEAR and STANDARD_ID=1 group by STUDENT_ID
SV_SumFunction.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select sum(MARKS_SECURED) as TOTAL_MARKS_SECURED, STUDENT_ID from RESULTS where ACADEMIC_YEAR=:ACADEMIC_YEAR and STANDARD_ID=1 group by STUDENT_ID) wmTempTable

SV_UnionAll.name: SV_UnionAll
SV_UnionAll.queryString: select * from EMPLOYEE_DETAILS UNION ALL select * FROM STUDENT_DETAILS ORDER BY CITY
SV_UnionAll.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select * from EMPLOYEE_DETAILS UNION ALL select * FROM STUDENT_DETAILS ORDER BY CITY) wmTempTable

SV_UpperFunction.name: SV_UpperFunction
SV_UpperFunction.countQueryString: select count(*) from (select UCASE(FIRSTNAME),UPPER(LASTNAME) from EMPLOYEE_DETAILS) wmTempTable
